----------------------------------------------------------
Prerequisite
----------------------------------------------------------

In terminal install this modules

1)pip install selenium

2)pip install tweepy

3)pip install bs4

4)download google chrome web drive and give its path in the file. 


--------------------------------------------------
Execution of the program
------------------------------------------------------
Used python 2.7 and linux system for program writing 

1)Run the file main_webscraping.py 

(give the exact  path for the google chrome web driver inn that file ) 

2) output is stored in the output.txt


-----------------------------------------------------
Modules used in the python program
----------------------------------------------------------

1) selenium 
(download chrome webdriver and give the path to it, in the program) 
It is used to load the webpage

2) Beautifil soup
It is used to extract the information from the html data

3) tweepy
It is used to connect to the twitter and get the tweets 

